Also added a restriction on search by date so users can only search for future dates.

On HomePage: Minor aesthetic changes On Results Panels: Put values from db to corresponding labels Handles the case of no search results Added venue address Design changes
Missing only the multiple artists(now showing only one) :)

Added Upload image to event and band
Band.java : changes on constructors Event.java : same EventOrganizerView.java: -Upload Button working -with edited filters -Image name saved on db -Image copied from user dir to project dir -Added label to show file name uploaded -Added MsgBox if no image is uploaded

NewBokingView.java: -Upload Button working - with edited filters -Image name saved on db -Image copied from user dir to project dir -Added label to show file name uploaded -Added MsgBox if no image is uploaded

ResultPanel.java : ActionListener to Book Tickets button

NewBookingView is *almost* ready.
Connected the search result with the view, populated the fields, calculated prices and totals, took a ridiculous amount of time to add some new labels and resize some others -_-
Missing a new class similar to ResultPanel to make the band panel, since we don't have a fixed number of bands anymore and *kinda important* the action listener for the Proceed to Booking.
I'll also try to make a text file with things missing or not working properly and also a list with completed classes-views.
Enjoy your vacation <3

Msg before booking changes depanding on users payment method Button is inactive if the user has picked no tickets, or if there aren't enough available.
On to Booking History :)

Booking History half way there(have to make the table pretty)
Minor changes in the other classes. New classes are support for existing ones :)
